title: $:/plugins/flancast90/speech-to-text/usage

!!! Settings

See the ~ControlPanel tab "Speech to Text" for all possible settings

!!! VoiceCommands

It's possible to create your own voice commands. To do so, follow these simple instructions:

* Create a tiddler and tag it with <<tag-pill "$:/tags/VoiceCommand">>
* Fill its ''text'' field with the desired `actions` that should be triggered
* Fill its `voice-commands` field with a ''list'' of voice commands
* Save the tiddler
